Pinn et al. 1999a
); mouthpart morphology and mouthpart setal fringes (
Pinn et al. 1999b
); functional response in filter feeding ( Lindahl & Baden 1997 ); oxygen transporting properties of heamocyanin (
Taylor et al. 2000
).

